name: Jimi Hendrix
description: Experimenting with process, changing everything, trying to embody the things I admire about this man. His music has inspired me endlessly and I hope this painting inspires creativity in your own life. Best viewed with your favorite Hendrix track playing in the background. Painted from scratch in photoshop, finished in Procreate. No filters, no overlay, no paintover, just 2 brushes and a blank canvas.
